### Trigger Unhandled Exception (requires Superadmin role)
# Expected: 500 Internal Server Error with a standard JSON error response.
# Requires a valid 'Superadmin' JWT token.
GET {{hostAddress}}/api/Faculty/throw-exception
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{superadminToken}}

